  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find yourself trapped inside this magical dome, formed by the 4 elements of nature: water, earth, air, and fire. To escape, you must explore your surroundings carefully, unravel enigmas, and solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.poster.avif?t=1741742927\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.webm?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.mp4?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore however you want, in your own time, in whatever order you want, and undo the magic of each of the 4 elements, one at a time, by finding and reaching their respective totems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.poster.avif?t=1741742927\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.webm?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.mp4?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a first-person perspective, you will have to use logic, think outside the box, and interact with the environment in unusual ways if you want to escape this mysterious magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First person perspective;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D movement;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free, non-linear exploration;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Logic puzzles;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Environmental puzzles;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-5 hours of gameplay;  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D pixel art stylized graphics</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find yourself trapped inside this magical dome, formed by the 4 elements of nature: water, earth, air, and fire. To escape, you must explore your surroundings carefully, unravel enigmas, and solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.poster.avif?t=1741742927\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.webm?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/cbe2dac3b5a9bc47d5a106f47c1a640b.mp4?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore however you want, in your own time, in whatever order you want, and undo the magic of each of the 4 elements, one at a time, by finding and reaching their respective totems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.poster.avif?t=1741742927\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.webm?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191420/extras/c5950f76851f93fbc5d2ec4a508c936d.mp4?t=1741742927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a first-person perspective, you will have to use logic, think outside the box, and interact with the environment in unusual ways if you want to escape this mysterious magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First person perspective;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D movement;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free, non-linear exploration;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Logic puzzles;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Environmental puzzles;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-5 hours of gameplay;  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D pixel art stylized graphics</p></li></ul>",
